Ing '''''Garcinia''''' metung yang [[genus]] da reng [[tanaman]] ning [[family (biology)|family]] [[Clusiaceae]], a tubu king [[Asia]], [[Australia]], deng dakeng mauli at malisangan king [[Africa]], at [[Polynesia]]. Maki bilang lang limang pulu anggang atlung dalan (50-300) deng species da reng dutung at palumpung (shrubs) a evergreen (e milalako bulung) a kayabe kaniting genus.  [[Dioecious]] ya iti, at [[:en:apomictic]] la reng mapilan kareng kayang sangkap o elementu. 

